description: The very first thing you notice with Jett are his lips…and apparently, people like commenting on them, “They tell me straight up, DSL. Dick. Sucking. Lips.” He’s a bit on the wild side; partying and getting into trouble, so living life to the fullest is definitely his thing. He’s certainly living on the edge jerking off on camera for us, so let’s see where this experience brings him…
title: Jett
